  <ul class="reference-list">
    <li>Cialdini, R.B. (2006). <em>Influence: The Psychology of Persuasion</em> (Revised Ed.). Harper Business. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/006124189X">Amazon</a></li>
    <li>Cialdini, R.B. (2016). <em>Pre-Suasion: A Revolutionary Way to Influence and Persuade</em>. Simon & Schuster. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1501109790">Amazon</a></li>
